

# ğŸ  House Price Prediction using Machine Learning

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project predicts **house prices** based on multiple features such as area, bedrooms, bathrooms, location, condition, and more using **Machine Learning Regression models**.

It includes:

* Data analysis (EDA)
* Feature preprocessing
* Baseline and advanced models
* Model evaluation
* Model saving
* Interactive Command Line Interface (CLI) for predictions

The goal is to build an **end-user friendly system** where anyone can enter house details and get a predicted price.

