## ğŸš€ Features

âœ” Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
âœ” Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
âœ” Linear Regression (Baseline Model)
âœ” Random Forest Regressor (Improved Model)
âœ” Performance Evaluation (MAE & RMSE)
âœ” Saved ML Pipeline
âœ” Interactive CLI Prediction Tool
âœ” Feature Importance Visualization
âœ” Metrics Export (JSON)

---

## ğŸ“Š Dataset Information

The dataset contains the following features:

| Feature   | Type        | Description         |
| --------- | ----------- | ------------------- |
| Area      | Numerical   | House area (sqft)   |
| Bedrooms  | Numerical   | Number of bedrooms  |
| Bathrooms | Numerical   | Number of bathrooms |
| Floors    | Numerical   | Number of floors    |
| YearBuilt | Numerical   | Construction year   |
| Location  | Categorical | House location      |
| Condition | Categorical | House condition     |
| Garage    | Categorical | Garage availability |
| Price     | Target      | House price         |

