## ğŸ’» CLI Prediction Tool

An interactive command-line tool is provided for end users.

### Run the CLI Tool

```bash
python predict_house_price_cli.py
```

### Example Usage

```
ğŸ  House Price Prediction CLI

Enter Area in square feet (e.g., 2500): 2500
Enter Number of Bedrooms (e.g., 3): 3
Enter Number of Bathrooms (e.g., 2): 2
Enter Number of Floors (e.g., 2): 2
Enter Year Built (e.g., 2015): 2015
Enter Location (Urban, Suburban, Downtown, Rural): Urban
Enter Condition (Excellent, Good, Fair, Poor): Good
Enter Garage (Yes/No): Yes
```

### Output

```
Predicted House Price: $345,000
Estimated Price Range: $310,500 - $379,500
```

