## ğŸ§  Machine Learning Pipeline

The project uses a complete ML pipeline:

1. Data preprocessing
2. Missing value handling
3. Encoding categorical features
4. Scaling numerical features
5. Model training
6. Evaluation
7. Saving pipeline

Implemented using:

* ColumnTransformer
* Pipeline (sklearn)

